You are given a positive integer n. Find the sum of the numbers 1 + 2 + 3 + ... + n

Write a function named sum that takes n as an argument and returns the sum of the numbers 1 through n.

Examples:
sum (1) must return 1;
sum (2) must return 3;
sum (3) should return 6;
sum (10) should return 55.


Solution:

function sum(n){
  let s = 0;
  for(let i = 1; i <= n; i++){
      s = s + i;
  }
  return s;
}
